Class Configuration

    • Model.Game.Configuration

  • public class Configuration
extends java.lang.Object
    This class contains a number of constant values that are used throughout the project. Containing them in a single class makes for easy adjustments and, in my opinion, cleaner code. Created by Martijn on 11-1-2016.
